 suggests that the excess emission may be due to\nintracluster gas accreted in the gravitational well of a massive galaxy. We\ninvestigate this and other possibilities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Jun 2011 10:21:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 Aug 2011 15:06:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-28"}
